snippet.title: CAT COMPILATION that DESERVES AN OSCAR! - You will LAUGH YOUR BUTT OFF
snippet.description:
Cats and kittens are the best and the funniest animals on Earth! They make us laugh all the time! We are never bored with cats! The most impossible try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look at all these cats and kittens how they fail, behave, meow, spin, jump... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
